   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="edition" ana="#b1" subtype="transcription" xml:id="caes0107.transcription" corresp="#caes0107.translation">
            <p>
               <expan>
                  <abbr>Imp</abbr>
                  <ex>eratori</ex>
               </expan>
               <expan>
                  <abbr>Caes</abbr>
                  <ex>ari</ex>
               </expan>
               <lb/>
               <expan>
                  <abbr>M</abbr>
                  <ex>arco</ex>
               </expan> Antonio<lb/>Gordiano<lb/>filio <expan>
                  <abbr>Aug</abbr>
                  <ex>usti</ex>
               </expan>
               <lb/>Semproniano<lb/>Romano<lb/>Africano<lb/>pio <expan>
                  <abbr>fel</abbr>
                  <ex>ici</ex>
               </expan>
               <expan>
                  <abbr>Aug</abbr>
                  <ex>usto</ex>
               </expan>
               <lb/>
               <expan>
                  <abbr>pontif</abbr>
                  <ex>ici</ex>
               </expan>
               <expan>
                  <abbr>trib</abbr>
                  <ex>unicia</ex>
               </expan>
               <lb/>
               <expan>
                  <abbr>pot</abbr>
                  <ex>estate</ex>
               </expan>
               <expan>
                  <abbr>co</abbr>
                  <ex>n</ex>
                  <abbr>s</abbr>
                  <ex>uli</ex>
               </expan>
               <lb/>
               <expan>
                  <abbr>pro</abbr>
                  <ex>consule</ex>
               </expan>.
		  </p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" ana="#b1" xml:id="caes0107.translation" corresp="#caes0107.transcription">
            <p>To <rs type="admTitle">Imperator </rs>
               <rs type="admTitle">Caesar </rs>
               <name>
                  <persName xml:lang="la " ref="persons.xml#caes0107p01">Marcus </persName>
                  <persName xml:lang="la " ref="persons.xml#caes0107p02">Antonius </persName>
                  <persName xml:lang="la " ref="persons.xml#caes0107p03">Gordianus </persName>
                  <persName xml:lang="la " ref="persons.xml#caes0107p04">Sempronianus </persName>
                  <persName xml:lang="la " ref="persons.xml#caes0107p05">Romanus </persName>
                  <persName xml:lang="la " ref="persons.xml#caes0107p06">Africanus </persName>
               </name>, dutiful and happy <name>
                  <persName xml:lang="la " ref="persons.xml#caes0107p07">Augustus </persName>
               </name>, son of <name>
                  <persName xml:lang="la " ref="persons.xml#caes0107p08">Augustus </persName>
               </name>, <rs type="admTitle">pontifex</rs>, with <rs type="admTitle">tribunician power</rs>, <rs type="admTitle">consul</rs>, <rs type="admTitle">proconsul</rs>.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
      <back>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>One of a group of milestones. Dimensions given are for height of milestone. Milestone is 0.38 m in diameter. The inscription was painted in red over a plastered surface.</p>
